content: This is quite good. A step up from the former version. You have to be quick to catch what's said and recording if possible is a good thing for play back extra confirmation. Yet you can get Real Time EVP with this!  And it's not to overloaded with sounds so you have a chance to digest.  If you want more just come out of the app leaving it live and go back in and press start again for double sound or more.  Has a nice quality clear sound to the frequencies.  It's a good app and cheap too for what it can do and you should get many results with this and quite consistently also.  There are a few vague sound words but if you wait for the energy to be allowed to build up through its systems and not jump on every word you hear and let it settle a bit you should find it works well.
replyContent: Thank you for your detailed review and sharing your professional experience and helpful ideas. That was wonderful to hear.
